<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tạrk ạlʿạlm klẗ wrạyạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- tạrk ạlʿạlm klẗ wrạyạ wkl kẖṭyẗ mn jwạyạ

[V2]
 kl kẖṭyẗ sknt fyạ wạkẖlt mkạnk mn jwạyạ

[V3]
 1- nsytk ạyạm lạ tḥṣy wdwrt ʿly tʿby bdlt ạlạyd ạlly tʿzy bạlsẖr ạlly ạḥzny

[V4]
 wbʿtrf ạny tʿbt fy bʿdk wạtmnyt ạrjʿ lw ạkwn ʿbdk

[V5]
 wrjʿt lqytk mstnyny bdmwʿy bkyt wqwltlk

[V6]
 2- trkt mṣdr ḥyạty wḥfrt ạbạr llmwt ạṣbḥt ʿbd lsẖhwạty ạlly ạnạ byhạ bạmwt

[V7]
 wmsẖyt wrạʾ ʿạlm klẗ mạ ynfʿ lkn ṣwtk bạlnʿmẗ qạlly ạrjʿ

[V8]
 wrjʿt lqytk mstnyny bdmwʿy bkyt wqwltlk

[V9]
 3- rjʿt lnfsy wqwlt ạnạ hạqwlk ạkẖṭạ̉t sạmḥny yạrb wạrḥmny ʿly kl kẖṭyẗ ʿmlt

[V10]
 nwyt brjwʿ wjạy hnạ wbqwlk ʿạyz ạʿysẖ kl ạyạmy bqrbk

[V11]
 wrjʿt lqytk mstnyny bdmwʿy bkyt wqwltlk</lyrics>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10336</hymn_number>
</song>